Edit or Remove Review
To remove your review:
Go to your profile.
Click the ellipses (...) button at the top right corner of the review box.
Remove my rating to a listing
To remove your rating:
Click here.
Select your rating.
Owner Asking Traveler for Review Removal
Tripadvisor absolutely does not condone threats or bullying of reviewers, and you should contact us if this ever happens.

